        <li><strong>Deadline Pressure:</strong> Project deadline approaching</li>
        <li><strong>Client Demand:</strong> Client needs crane immediately</li>
        <li><strong>Growth Opportunity:</strong> Business expanding fast</li>
        <li><strong>Seasonal Rush:</strong> Peak construction period</li>
